  "title": "Waitakere Ranges Regional Park: Kitekite Falls",
  "summary": "周末闲逛时间去了西区，顺便去趟Costco。 听说这个步道最近刚刚翻新，所以过来看看。 其实翻新之前没来过，这 […]",
  "content": "<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image-14.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>周末闲逛时间去了西区，顺便去趟Costco。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image-4.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>听说这个步道最近刚刚翻新，所以过来看看。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image-12.png?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>其实翻新之前没来过，这是我第一次来。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image-5.png?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>路不长，但是有一段需要小心涉水。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image-7.png?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>后半程道路分叉，一边通向瀑布底，一边去瀑布顶。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image-8.png?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>植物很茂盛，这个季节甚至有点冷。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image-13.png?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>总体来说不算难走。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image-9.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>水很清澈，花纹很漂亮。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image-6.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>上午去的人不多，很安静。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image-10.png?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>阳光洒下来，心情会变好。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image-11.png?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>",
  "image": "https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image-14.png",
